<!DOCTYPE html>

<html class="light" lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport" />
    <title>B E O - Guía paso a paso</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "surface-tint": "#117278",
                        "on-surface-variant": "#64748b",
                        "surface-container-highest": "#e0e3e3",
                        "surface-bright": "#ffffff",
                        "secondary": "#476366",
                        "on-secondary-fixed": "#012022",
                        "inverse-surface": "#112021",
                        "error": "#ba1a1a",
                        "background": "#f6f8f8",
                        "surface-container-high": "#e6e9e9",
                        "surface": "#ffffff",
                        "on-tertiary": "#ffffff",
                        "on-primary-container": "#117278",
                        "surface-container-lowest": "#ffffff",
                        "primary-fixed-dim": "#83d3da",
                        "secondary-fixed-dim": "#aeccce",
                        "tertiary-fixed-dim": "#ffb68b",
                        "on-error": "#ffffff",
                        "secondary-fixed": "#c9e8eb",
                        "tertiary": "#78411b",
                        "on-secondary": "#ffffff",
                        "on-primary": "#ffffff",
                        "on-secondary-fixed-variant": "#2f4b4e",
                        "on-primary-fixed": "#002022",
                        "surface-dim": "#d7dbda",
                        "error-container": "#ffdad6",
                        "on-secondary-container": "#4d696c",
                        "on-primary-fixed-variant": "#004f54",
                        "on-tertiary-fixed-variant": "#6e3913",
                        "surface-variant": "#f8fafc",
                        "on-tertiary-fixed": "#321300",
                        "on-surface": "#0f172a",
                        "primary-container": "#1172781a",
                        "inverse-primary": "#83d3da",
                        "inverse-on-surface": "#f6f8f8",
                        "tertiary-fixed": "#ffdbc8",
                        "tertiary-container": "#955830",
                        "surface-container-low": "#f6f8f8",
                        "on-background": "#0f172a",
                        "on-tertiary-container": "#ffe1d1",
                        "outline": "#117278",
                        "primary-fixed": "#9ff0f6",
                        "on-error-container": "#93000a",
                        "surface-container": "#ebeeee",
                        "outline-variant": "#e2e8f0",
                        "primary": "#117278",
                        "secondary-container": "#c9e8eb"
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "headline": ["Inter"],
                        "body": ["Inter"],
                        "label": ["Inter"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: { "DEFAULT": "0.25rem", "lg": "0.5rem", "xl": "0.75rem", "full": "9999px" },
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        .material-symbols-outlined {
            font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>

<body class="bg-background text-on-background antialiased selection:bg-primary/20">
    <%- include('../../Partials/header') %>
    <main class="pt-24 pb-20">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-6">
                Tu camino al <span class="text-primary">éxito profesional</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Descubre cómo B E O conecta a los mejores expertos con proyectos que transforman realidades. Sigue
                nuestra guía paso a paso.
            </p>
        </section>
        <!-- Step-by-Step Vertical Timeline / Blocks -->
        <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 relative">
            <!-- Connector Line (Desktop) -->
            <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-primary/10 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
            <div class="space-y-12 md:space-y-24 relative">
                <!-- Step 1 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-16">
                    <div class="flex-1 md:text-right order-2 md:order-1">
                        <span
                            class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Paso
                            1</span>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Regístrate</h2>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Crea tu perfil profesional en segundos. Ya
                            seas un experto buscando nuevos retos o una empresa con visión, el primer paso es unirte a
                            nuestra comunidad exclusiva.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex-shrink-0 order-1 md:order-2">
                        <div
                            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-surface shadow-lg border border-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all duration-500">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl" data-icon="person_add">person_add</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 order-3 hidden md:block">
                        <img class="rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant w-full h-48 object-cover"
                            data-alt="close-up of a high-end laptop with a modern registration form on screen, soft morning light in a minimal professional office"
                            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA90vWjjW6HNnVvZADnmv3Dl4sgpAOVxyioAhT5qIrlNcFhkpbXSAD4zAwh4yxnEoP6cvuHfHgR9ekEWCW5h8n1-1bxmGgnI0hAC-E5QithAaOIGhjlBhbR6R3weuSIdi-iPfzWcm8ql1GJQ6J_j0eHb8fjfE3t50aVEoDN-dlqePpCpPXnzOYN394Wij4ban_Kb4WCNbSVmQSZUAIVbjJBwz-diy2-o2qC_f33hy4WrUARd0uyqvarYPNSgB6BgXbHJTBxcFc03vE" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 2 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-16">
                    <div class="flex-1 hidden md:block">
                        <img class="rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant w-full h-48 object-cover"
                            data-alt="collaborative workspace with diverse professionals looking at a large screen displaying search results and data analytics"
                            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDIPdrNxfgK1RI4my3KQWduKdIgNVEhejQd3KaMnXlW4x4-CvM4bjr5D0zclipTqlsfD55NAUWhR0heRLR2uUBEu2CiV2wto1ACA_E2zTDuql4r79XuP_7IaBEs8Eh8_kTr0fisy8Fr0kKPQBYJ9uPuqP6ZgCvNWe1b2RvQqtU4QSgPVMc_-Jdaz3S9-hjIstmMM3bvKg_yC_b_bZUtxIo80tx4camsnKcbKwvUbt1ocRAUIMIW3T1GU-cXG86al_Hw3fnLSZOBlCk" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex-shrink-0">
                        <div
                            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-surface shadow-lg border border-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all duration-500">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl" data-icon="search">search</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 text-left">
                        <span
                            class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Paso
                            2</span>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Encuentra al experto ideal</h2>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Utiliza nuestras herramientas de búsqueda
                            avanzada y filtros inteligentes para filtrar por especialidad, ubicación y experiencia
                            comprobada en San Juan del Río.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 3 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-16">
                    <div class="flex-1 md:text-right order-2 md:order-1">
                        <span
                            class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Paso
                            3</span>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Contrata y paga seguro</h2>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Nuestra plataforma garantiza transacciones
                            seguras. Los fondos se mantienen protegidos hasta que el trabajo es entregado
                            satisfactoriamente, brindando paz mental a ambas partes.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex-shrink-0 order-1 md:order-2">
                        <div
                            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-surface shadow-lg border border-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all duration-500">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl"
                                data-icon="verified_user">verified_user</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 order-3 hidden md:block">
                        <img class="rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant w-full h-48 object-cover"
                            data-alt="top view of two hands shaking firmly over a clean wooden desk with a digital tablet showing a signed contract"
                            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCvcWsxr7ICPzWZJtJYVwa3emLopqvgcFLAs3BJ4MTgc9xhvN2r3vwUtWj24OyTAIgtpywoLHS3j97RWR08zuOg-NoRueu2y03_ikYzlT3cfgdt8OQO7hHIAgAjDXYDQgXFQTdiM4tZ-_PWD_JL2-rQUe0nSTIy3hAXJGoTbaaEUsmryflQLPKBI-lUz1E0Otkkbg3XeGEvLKm2xVFKGDo7Y-aT6kppkbSrs_yUKUhzj1MxS7jpUERS63HYaQefmtwSSfyadxuV0lI" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 4 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-16">
                    <div class="flex-1 hidden md:block">
                        <img class="rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant w-full h-48 object-cover"
                            data-alt="close up of a professional hand giving a five star rating on a sleek mobile app interface with teal accents"
                            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAYlDNX5lM1hw7ZPmtiYWY_dB6Sm8TRWt0EcGxuBcwEZqPhPttwhic7Vp1WlBkdutIQeyOLcMePahQkwdAjA6b8FaxABCZb0n4dnRCzebNL1AI2d9kGLKZWJxMudqD0HtWrU7X68_1RuRlvfZqoOTvyzYKCjg7jLRe0SnzNiuJaUtpTFVJbgIfCrm_LoIwFBsMbDMY3SpGrtlhG971b_UYh6jVuECWGyqF8DxU7nEuMTqUb-XFjR6H52BgapgGYymABotr0uCl57yM" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex-shrink-0">
                        <div
                            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-surface shadow-lg border border-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all duration-500">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl" data-icon="star">star</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 text-left">
                        <span
                            class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Paso
                            4</span>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Califica el trabajo</h2>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Tu opinión construye la confianza. Califica
                            la calidad del servicio y ayuda a otros usuarios a tomar mejores decisiones mientras
                            impulsas el crecimiento de los mejores talentos.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 mt-24">
            <div class="bg-primary p-8 md:p-16 rounded-3xl text-center text-white shadow-lg">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 tracking-tight">¿Listo para empezar?</h2>
                <p class="text-primary-fixed/80 text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">Únete hoy a la red profesional más
                    importante de la región y lleva tus proyectos al siguiente nivel.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                    <button
                        class="bg-surface text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold shadow-xl hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all active:scale-95">
                        Crear Cuenta Gratis
                    </button>
                    <button
                        class="bg-white/10 text-white border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-white/20 transition-all">
                        Hablar con un Asesor
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../../Partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>